author: Huawei
description:
#OmanAirports is marking major milestones in aviation history at Muscat International Airport. In partnership with #Huawei, the airport has launched the world’s first Intelligent Campus Showcase, a milestone that ushers in a new era of aviation innovation.
 
This intelligent campus brings together ultra-fast #WiFi7, smart operations, and enhanced security, raising the bar for passenger experience, operational resilience, and airport efficiency worldwide.
 
Explore how this breakthrough sets a global benchmark in smart airports: https://bit.ly/4pb053s
title: Oman Airports and Huawei Showcase World-First Intelligent Campus
